citation.case_name: City of San Antonio v. Stucky, Dba Bill's Wrecker Service

html:
536 U.S. 936

CITY OF SAN ANTONIO ET AL.
v.
STUCKY, DBA BILL'S WRECKER SERVICE, ET AL.

No. 01-1028.

Supreme Court of the United States.

June 24, 2002.

1

C. A. 5th Cir. Certiorari granted, judgment vacated, and case remanded for further consideration in light of Columbus v. Ours Garage & Wrecker Service, Inc., ante, p. 424. Reported below: 260 F. 3d 424.
